query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.favorite_count >= 0 AND q.favorite_count <= 10000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('angularjs-ng-repeat',
'angularjs-scope',
'apache-camel',
'google-calendar-api',
'gorm',
'graph-algorithm',
'hex',
'itextsharp',
'jsonp',
'kivy',
'office-js',
'postman',
'single-page-application',
'tcl');
